      "content": "Interesting. When you mention that Profile B's \"changing demographics\" and \"shifts in community composition\" introduce unpredictability and volatility, what specific types of demographic shifts are you thinking of that create that risk? Are you suggesting that certain types of population changes are inherently more destabilizing for property values than others?",
